by javiereguiluz at 2016-03-14T19:37:30Z

**Update**

Since this change can break things, I plan to release the `1.12.0` version containing only this change. In 074988c I've improved the error message of the "Undefined entity" exception to add a link to the changelog of the future 1.12.0 version. There we'll explain the change and the simple solution to fix it.

Hopefully this change won't cause much pain. :pray:

